1. *Upoznao* sam ga pre nekoliko godina na putovanju. (I met him a few years ago during a trip.)
2. Ona je *upoznala* njegovu sestru pre dve godine. (She met his sister two years ago.)
3. *Upoznali* smo se preko društvenih mreža. (We met through social media.)
4. *Upoznavali* smo ljude sa raznih strana sveta. (We were meeting people from different parts of the world.)
5. *Upoznali* smo se pre dve nedelje. (We met two weeks ago.)